Global Video Compressor Market Insights
Video Compressor Market size was valued at USD 5.2 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 11.3 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 10.2% from 2024 to 2030.

Video Compressor Market Overview
The global video compressor market size was valued at USD 2.4 billion in 2024 and is expected to expand at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 8.3% from 2025 to 2030. The increasing demand for high-definition (HD) and 4K video streaming, coupled with the rising adoption of video content across various platforms, is expected to drive market growth. The need for efficient video compression technologies to support faster content delivery, particularly in mobile applications and online streaming services, is fueling the expansion of the video compressor market. As data traffic continues to grow, particularly due to video-on-demand (VOD) services and video conferencing, the market for video compression technologies will see significant growth globally.

